                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Tout pâle, et l'a couvert d'un indigent affront.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Celle qu'on appelait la charmante, l'heureuse,",
